<p><strong>Development system</strong></p>

<p>Raspberry pi with the PiBang distribution</p>

<ul>
  <li>Powersupply for the Raspberry pi</li>
  <li>XAMPP server on the Raspberry pi</li>
  <li>Arduino  IDE version 1.0.5</li>
  <li>Arduino UNO Rev. 3 with Ethernet shield</li>
  <li>Red 5mm LED</li>
  <li>Resistor of  330 Ohm</li>
  <li>Switch and wires</li>
  <li>Powered  USB hub</li>
  <li>HDMI capable monitor &amp; HDMI cable</li>
  <li>USB keyboard and mouse</li>
  <li>UTP cable  for the internet connection of the Raspberry pi</li>
  <li>UTP cable  for the internet connection of the Arduino  Ethernet shield</li>
</ul>

